'''山達基教會'''（'''Church of Scientology'''）是[[新興宗教|新興宗教]][[山達基|山達基]]的組織。{{tsl|en|Church of Scientology International|國際山達基教會}}（Church of Scientology International）是全球所有山達基教會的總會，負責國際層級的管理和傳教事宜。而世界各地的山達基教會則是各自營運，並擁有自己的董事會及執行長。<ref>{{cite book|title= description of the Scientology ecclesiastical structure on www.rtc.org|last= Melton|first= J. Gordon|authorlink= J. Gordon Melton|date= Sep 2000|publisher= Rtc.org|quote= |url= http://www.rtc.org/intro/pg002.html|accessdate= 2011-11-22|archive-date= 2011-09-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110927011050/http://www.rtc.org/intro/pg002.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>

全球第一間山達基教會創立於1953年12月，由[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]所創。

==理念==
創辦人[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]解釋「山達基」名稱的起源自拉丁文"scio"，意思是「認識與區辨」。
<ref>{{cite journal |title=Rethinking Scientology A Thorough Analysis of L. Ron Hubbard’s Formulation of Therapy and Religion in Dianetics and Scientology, 1950–1986 |journal=Alternative Spirituality and Religion Review |date=June 24, 2016 |last=Christensen |first=Dorthe Refslund |doi=10.5840/asrr201662323 |accessdate=2017-01-25}}</ref>
然而創辦人[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]的組織在美國遭受相當大的反彈。1951年元月，紐澤西人體試驗者委員會（<font color="#000000">the New Jersey Board of Medical Examiners</font>）控告[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]的基金會「無照教授醫學」。
<ref>{{cite book |last=Reitman |first1=Janet |title=Inside Scientology: The Story of America's Most Secretive Religion |url=https://archive.org/details/insidescientolog0000reit_r2z9 |publisher=Houghton Mifflin Harcourt |year=2011 |isbn=9780547549231 }}</ref>
<ref name="books.google.com">{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=umep6P6dYLAC&pg=PA532 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-05 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903232811/https://books.google.com/books?id=umep6P6dYLAC&pg=PA532 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]的追隨者曾在1970年代秘密進行山達基教全球「漂白」計畫，透過竊取各國政府對於山達基教的負面文件來達成目的。此計畫是美國有史以來最大宗的間諜賄賂案。後來幾位山達基教的高層被美國法院以妨礙司法公平、竊取政府文件、擅闖政府機關定罪。<ref name="urban2006">Urban, Hugh B. "Fair Game: Secrecy, Security, and the Church of Scientology in Cold War America." ''[[Journal_of_the_American_Academy_of_Religion|Journal of the American Academy of Religion]]'' '''74''':2 (2006)</ref><ref name="urban2008">{{cite journal|last=Urban|first=Hugh B.|year=2008|title=Secrecy and New Religious Movements: Concealment, Surveillance, and Privacy in a New Age of Information|journal=Religion Compass|publisher=Wiley |volume=2|issue=1|pages=66–83|issn=1749-8171|doi=10.1111/j.1749-8171.2007.00052.x|ref=harv}}</ref>[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]的相關組織目前在德國被判定為「違反憲法」("anti-constitutional sect"/''verfassungsfeindliche Sekte'')；在法國則初步被認定為「邪教」。<ref name="spiegel.de">{{Cite web |url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/hubbard-s-church-unconstitutional-germany-prepares-to-ban-scientology-a-522052.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-05 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225144219/http://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/hubbard-s-church-unconstitutional-germany-prepares-to-ban-scientology-a-522052.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="assemblee-nationale.fr">{{Cite web |url=http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/rap-enq/r2468.asp |title=National Assembly of France report No. 2468 |accessdate=2017-03-05 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225144222/http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/rap-enq/r2468.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>A 1995 [[French_Parliament|parliamentary]] report lists Scientology groups as [[cult|cult]]s, and in its 2006 report [[MIVILUDES|MIVILUDES]] similarly classified Scientology organizations as a dangerous [[cult|cult]]</ref><ref name="NouvelObs">[http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/societe/20090525.OBS8000/le-point-sur-l-eglise-de-scientologie.html Le point sur l'Eglise de Scientologie] {{Wayback|url=http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/societe/20090525.OBS8000/le-point-sur-l-eglise-de-scientologie.html |date=20170206065202 }}, Le Nouvel Observateur</ref><ref name="r2468">[http://www.assemblee-nationale.org/rap-enq/r2468.asp Rapport d'enquête n°2468 de l'Assemblée nationale] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503110658/http://www.assemblee-nationale.org/rap-enq/r2468.asp |date=2007-05-03 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/dossiers/sectes/r1687.pdf |title=Rapport MILS 1999 |accessdate=2017-03-05 |archive-date=2010-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101122034631/http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/dossiers/sectes/r1687.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.lemonde.fr/societe/article/2012/02/02/une-condamnation-historique-contre-l-eglise-de-scientologie_1637845_3224.html "Une condamnation historique" contre l'Eglise de scientologie] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/societe/article/2012/02/02/une-condamnation-historique-contre-l-eglise-de-scientologie_1637845_3224.html |date=20170426162701 }}, le Monde</ref><ref>[http://www.miviludes.gouv.fr/IMG/pdf/Report_Miviludes_2006.pdf Miviludes 2006 report (PDF)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809193839/http://www.miviludes.gouv.fr/IMG/pdf/Report_Miviludes_2006.pdf |date=2007-08-09 }}</ref><ref>Shermer, Michael. "Is Scientology a Cult?" Skeptic 17.1 (2011): 16-17. Retrieved January 21, 2016.</ref>

